snippet.title: TRLE Hall of Fame 2016  - The Lost Valley
snippet.description:
The Lost Valley - Author by JEYEM
final release version 1.5.6 (29-Dec-2001)
http://www.trle.net/sc/levelfeatures.php?lid=503
Tomb Raider Level Editor 100% walkthrough - The Lost Valley final release version 1.5.6
Kills: black scorpions/14(6+2+1+3+2), crocodiles/7(1+1+1+4), assassins/8(2+1+1+2+2).
Items: 39 (Include Crowbar, Uzis, Crossbow, Shotgun, Cartouche Piece 2, Guardian Key, Hand Of Orion, Canopic Jar 1, LaserSight, Cartouche Piece 1, Ba Cartouche, Revolver, Canopic Jar 2, Golden Vraeus, Golden Rose). Secrets 5/5
all kills, all pick-ups, no-scratch.

- Change to version 1.5.6. -
An audio folder and data folder exist when you defrost the zip file which downloaded from trle.net.
Replace the "valley.tr4" file of the data folder with version 1.5.6 or overwrite it.

Other level
Stunt In Underground
http://www.trle.net/sc/levelfeatures.php?lid=178
